      <title>华尔街的加密 ETF 热潮因 XRP 首次备案而加速</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/wall-street-s-crypto-etf-boom-gathers-pace-on-first-xrp-filing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 Bitwise Asset Management Inc. 成为第一家申请直接投资全球第七大数字代币 XRP 的基金之后，华尔街的 ETF 颠覆者再次敦促监管机构向大众开放加密货币热潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/wall-street-s-crypto-etf-boom-gathers-pace-on-first-xrp-filing</guid>
